# Aurel3 suggested cron entries

# Entry-scan cycle is driven by the OpenClaw agent-turn (aurel3-signal-cycle),
# which interprets the batch and calls openclaw_import + signal_scan itself.
# The old `openclaw_cycle` subprocess command has been removed.

# Watchlist review: more frequent than entry scans
30 10,14,18,20 * * 1-5 bash /root/aurel3/cron.sh watchlist_review

# Review matured recommendations on weekdays
0 21 * * 1-5 bash /root/aurel3/cron.sh review_signals

# Weekly summary
0 9 * * 0 bash /root/aurel3/cron.sh review_summary
